articles.author: Eli Watkins, CNN
articles.title: NYT: Mueller looking through Trump's tweets
articles.description: Special counsel Robert Mueller has been reviewing President Donald Trump's Twitter feed as part of the former FBI director's probe into obstruction of justice, The New York Times reported Thursday.

articles.title: Live: President Trump in Iowa and Illinois - CNNPolitics
articles.description: President Trump is traveling to Iowa and Illinois, as his administration faces a deadline to reunite migrant families separated at the border. Follow here for the latest.

articles.author: Sunlen Serfaty and Lauren Fox, CNN
articles.title: Conservative Rep. Jim Jordan to run for speaker
articles.description: Rep. Jim Jordan, a leader in the conservative House Freedom Caucus and former chairman of the group, told CNN he will announce his run for speaker of the House of Representatives in a letter to colleagues Thursday.

articles.title: CNN obtains secret Trump-Cohen audio recording - CNN Video
articles.description: Presidential candidate Donald Trump is heard on tape discussing with attorney Michael Cohen how they would buy the rights to a Playboy model's story about an alleged affair Trump had with her years earlier.

articles.title: Late night skewers Trump over Cohen recording - CNN Video
articles.description: Late-night hosts react to the secret recording aired by CNN of President Trump and his attorney Michael Cohen discussing how they would buy the rights to a Playboy model's story about an alleged affair.

articles.author: Jeremy Diamond and MJ Lee, CNN
articles.title: Cohen sent up flares, but Trump never came to help
articles.description: Cohen, the President's longtime attorney and adviser, agonized over the silent treatment he was getting from his former boss.

articles.author: John Avlon
articles.title: Donald Trump and the Ministry of Truth
articles.description: A snapshot of nine hours in the Trump administration shows how their increasingly absurd defense of the indefensible leads to a dangerous and Orwellian place, says John Avlon.

articles.title: Burnett: Trump is trying to save face  - CNN Video
articles.description: CNN's Erin Burnett asks why President Donald Trump decided to postpone his next meeting with Russian President Vladimir Putin.

articles.title: Cooper: Tapes reveal another campaign lie - CNN Video
articles.description: CNN's Anderson Cooper breaks down the taped conversations between President Donald Trump and his former personal attorney Michael Cohen.

articles.author: Marshall Cohen, CNN
articles.title: Audio expert analyzes secret Trump-Cohen tape
articles.description: The debate over a secret recording between Donald Trump and his longtime attorney Michael Cohen continued Wednesday, with both sides offering different explanations of what was heard on the tape.
